Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.77,0:14:29.56,Flora,teks,0,0,0,,{\i1\pos(960,940)\fscy66\fscx66}Bebola Petir!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.65,0:14:42.78,Utama,Alphonse,0,0,0,,Kalau Bebola Petir tidak\Nberkesan, guna Tombak Ais!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.45,0:14:45.83,Utama,Alphonse,0,0,0,,Barisan hadapan, tingkatkan kebolehan fizikal!
