Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.09,0:15:06.47,Utama,Alphonse,0,0,0,,Berundur!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.47,0:15:08.31,Utama,Alphonse,0,0,0,,Lari!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.68,0:15:12.60,Roana,Roanna,0,0,0,,Kristina-sama!\NTolong berhati-hati.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.60,0:15:13.56,Flora,Christina,0,0,0,,Ya...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.56,0:15:14.77,Flora,Christina,0,0,0,,Flora?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.52,0:15:17.82,Roana,Roanna,0,0,0,,Saya pasti dia sudah melarikan diri.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.82,0:15:19.32,Roana,Roanna,0,0,0,,Kita juga patut pergi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.45,0:15:25.78,Flora,Flora,0,0,0,,Kamu tak apa-apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.30,0:15:50.60,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Tolong bawa dia dan pergi dari sini!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.89,0:15:51.72,Flora,Flora,0,0,0,,Rio-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.72,0:15:52.81,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Lekas!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.35,0:15:54.06,Flora,Flora,0,0,0,,Baik!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.06,0:15:55.14,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Sini!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.85,0:15:57.06,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Meh!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.91,0:16:07.74,Condong,Rio,0,0,0,,Keras...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.74,0:16:08.91,Condong,Rio,0,0,0,,Dan...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.91,0:16:09.66,Condong,Rio,0,0,0,,Laju!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.08,0:16:13.00,Condong,Rio,0,0,0,,Aku tak boleh mati di sini!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.00,0:16:15.96,Condong,Rio,0,0,0,,Tapi kenapa aku kembali selamatkan dia?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.38,0:16:21.34,Flora,Flora,0,0,0,,Hebatnya!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.95,0:16:49.49,Condong,Rio,0,0,0,,Sekarang.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.55,0:17:09.13,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Dah kenapa dengan raksasa itu—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.13,0:17:10.34,Roana,Roanna,0,0,0,,Flora-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.34,0:17:12.85,Roana,Roanna,0,0,0,,Flora-sama, kamu tak cedera?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.85,0:17:15.60,Flora,Flora,0,0,0,,Tak. M-Maafkan saya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.31,0:17:25.90,Condong,Reiss,0,0,0,,Wau, nampaknya aku dapat menyaksikan\Nperkara yang lebih menarik.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.90,0:17:27.44,Condong,Reiss,0,0,0,,Si rambut hitam...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.44,0:17:31.20,Condong,Reiss,0,0,0,,Adakah dia berketurunan\Norang dari wilayah Yagumo?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.20,0:17:35.08,Condong,Reiss,0,0,0,,Kalau begitu, masuk akal juga kalau\Ndia boleh menggunakan seni atma.
